baelaāyaṭakao abhyaāsa khaelamaā naepaālakao lagaāṭaāra ṭaesa्rao jaiṭa

kaāthamaādaaun, saāuna १

abhyaāsa khaelakaā laāgai baelaāyaṭa bhramaṇamaā rahaekao naepaālai raāstraiya kraikaeta taolailae klaba kraikaeta kanphraensalaāi (saisaisai) chaāra waikaetalae haraāekao chha । 

baelaāyaṭakao laṇa्danasa्ṭhaiṭa sa्taānamaora saisai maaiḍaānamaā gaeraāṭai bhaekao khaelamaā gharaelau taolai saisaisailaāi haraāepachhai naepaālalae lagaāṭaāra ṭaesa्rao jaiṭa haāṭa paāraekao hao । tasa jaiṭaera byaātaiŋa garaekao saisaisailae nairḍhaāraiṭa ५० obharamaā ७ waikaetakao ksaṭaimaā २२६ rana banaāekao ṭhaiyao । jawaāphai byaātaiŋamaā āekao naepaālalae ४६.१ obharamaā maāṭra chha waikaeta gaumaāunḍaai laksya bhaetaāyao । 

naepaālakao jaiṭamaā kapa्ṭaāna paārasa khadkaālae arḍhasaṭakaiya paārai khaela्ḍaai sarwaāḍhaika ६७ rana banaāe । ṭyasa्ṭaai, anaila maṇa्dalalae ४३, upakapa्ṭaāna jñaānaenḍa्ra mala्lalae ३६, saraḍa bhaesawaākaralae १९ ranakao yaogaḍaāna ḍaie bhanae awaijaiṭa rahanḍaai taolaikao jaiṭa naikaālaekaā raājau raijaāla ra raājau paulaāmailae kramasah wa्yakṭaigaṭa १७ ra १६ rana jaodae । ṭyasaaigarai wainaoḍa bhaṇa्daārailae chha ṭaṭhaā saāgara paunalae chaāra rana banaāe । 

yasaaghai saisaisailaāi raoknae kramamaā naepaālakaā saomapaāla kaāmai ra sanḍaipa laāmaichhaānaelae ḍaui÷ḍaui ṭaṭhaā kapa्ṭaāna paārasa ra karaṇa kaesailae eka÷eka waikaeta laie । 

āgaāmai mahainaā naeḍarala्yaāndasanga usakaai gharaelau maaiḍaānamaā waisa्wa kraikaeta laiga cha्yaāmpaiyanasaipa khaela्nae ṭayaāraimaā rahaekao naepaāla ahailae abhyaāsa khaelakaā laāgai baelaāyaṭamaā chha । naepaāla maeraolaebaona klabakao naimṭaomaā yasaai saāṭaā landana gaekao hao । 

yasaaghai bhaekaā ḍauwaai khaelamaā jaiṭa naikaāla्nae kramamaā naepaālalae phrai–phaoraesa्tara klabalaāi १२९ ranakao waisaāla anṭaralae haraāekao ṭhaiyao bhanae indaiyana jaimakhaānaālaāi २० ranalae paākhaā lagaāekao ṭhaiyao । raāsasa